{"tid":1841054,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"工業行動唔係只有全面罷工，可以停止所有非緊急醫療服務","createTime":"2020-01-25T06:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:50.000Z","uid":29625,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6437bef03b35acf334e25b531808ed593543dd","tid":1841054,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"明明四個醫療工會都係講緊<span style=\"color: orange;\">工業行動</span><br />\n唔係係特登偷換概念定係無心忽略<br />\n發覺呢2日好多罷工post都講到罷工=見死不救咁<br />\n但係實際上工業行動唔止全面罷工一個選擇<br />\n<br />\n以下係我自己google嘅結果，有錯嘅麻煩業內人士指正<br />\n以2015-16年英國junior doctor因為待遇問題而發起嘅工業行動例<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">醫生喺推遲/停止非緊急醫療服務嘅同時，係可以確保緊急服務正常運作:</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">The doctors are providing emergency cover only </span>during the 24-hour walkout, which got under way at 08:00 GMT.</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>In preparation for the action, hospital bosses across the country had:<br />\n- postponed 4,000 routine treatments, such as knee and hip replacements, some of which are on the days before and after the walkout<br />\n- cancelled many more appointments, check-ups and tests<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">prioritised cancer care to minimise the risk to those needing vital surgery and treatment</span><br />\n- told patients to use alternatives to hospital on the day of the strike where possible, such as pharmacies, NHS 111 and GPs</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/health-35286343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-35286343&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=c003ef1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-35286343&h=ef8f8865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/health-35286343</a><br />\n<br />\n而事後根據實際數字<br />\n死亡數字亦無因為工業行動而有明顯改變<br />\n<blockquote>The researchers said the number of recorded deaths did not change significantly during the strikes and was not higher than expected, due to relatively small numbers.</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.onmedica.com/newsArticle.aspx?id=1e4139f5-3007-4e74-bdfb-ccaac336a70c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.onmedica.com%2FnewsArticle.aspx%3Fid%3D1e4139f5-3007-4e74-bdfb-ccaac336a70c&d=u2pAR7e6RxUPEaw7qAEO%2FSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=65ae31ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.onmedica.com/newsArticle.aspx?id=1e4139f5-3007-4e74-bdfb-ccaac336a70c</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">以工業行動施壓有好大實際操作空間<br />\n話罷工會害死病人根本係偽命題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n工業行動最終目標係向政府施壓<br />\n要求當局正視疫情，採取實際措施防疫保障市民安全<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府面對疫情不作為，只係識用職責兩隻字將重擔推去醫護人員身上<br />\n呢種行動至係等同脅持病人，強逼醫護處理政府失職嘅爛攤子</span><br />\n罷工為嘅係唔止救助眼前病人，更係為廣大市民健康著想<br />\n唔該唔好再打稻草人批評醫護!"},{"pid":"4af51204d1424a9d1e96e8f372ab4e571581efcf","tid":1841054,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed55e837f8ca51f5a1f9497408d2e714dbc6e35","tid":1841054,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:47:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾標題無人睇"},{"pid":"527b1387a72c7a5d5de65c9554d32dd8e3373262","tid":1841054,"uid":129940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:51:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be8a56213edc2411d9ef85b8641afff1c5ad8efe","tid":1841054,"uid":38563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T06:53:56.000Z","msg":"我都覺<br />\n事實上都唔可能全院罷工<br />\n有三成人手都應付到d緊急case卦？"},{"pid":"6935092a24d8e8c31e0e90cbc659cd9281e82eb9","tid":1841054,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"不如由而家開始唔好再醫非香港人？"},{"pid":"a442be4327b1227baa0fc2291eccad7af9731c07","tid":1841054,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6935092a24d8e8c31e0e90cbc659cd9281e82eb9","tid":1841054,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"不如由而家開始唔好再醫非香港人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"其中一個選項"},{"pid":"0424a8b90f6dcd8120eacd99d919ef6c787b8846","tid":1841054,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df92b12306a01f6d3263c1acd865bf607106d32","tid":1841054,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:53:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"}]}